headline: National Union member: Shooting attack shows IDF should stay in territories
description: National Union member Uri Ariel said on Monday that a deadly West Bank shooting attack by terrorists showed that Israel must not carry out its pullout plan because the IDF's presence in the West Bank and Gaza is "the only way to prevent attacks by bloodthirsty killers like the ones we saw this morning." (Ilan Marciano)
articleBody: National Union member Uri Ariel said on Monday that a deadly West Bank shooting attack by terrorists showed that Israel must not carry out its pullout plan because the IDF's presence in the West Bank and Gaza is "the only way to prevent attacks by bloodthirsty killers like the ones we saw this morning." (Ilan Marciano)
title: מיכל ינאי מתלבשת על החופש הגדול: "כל הבגדים שלי עם כתמים"
